sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Uploader as Uploader
    actor Moderator as Moderator
    participant Server as Next.js Server
    participant Ext as Cloudinary / Gemini / Brevo
    participant DB as Database

    %% Upload Flow
    Note over Uploader,DB: 1. Note Upload Flow
    Uploader->>Uploader: Fill form & validate (Zod)
    Uploader->>Server: POST signCloudinaryPreset()
    Server-->>Uploader: Return preset & signature
    Uploader->>Ext: PUT image to Cloudinary
    Ext-->>Uploader: Return secure_url
    Uploader->>Server: saveNote(title, urls)
    Server->>DB: BEGIN TX: Insert note, files, resources
    Server->>DB: updateStreak(userId)
    Server-->>Uploader: Success

    %% Moderation Flow
    Note over Uploader,DB: 2. Moderation Flow
    Moderator->>Server: getPendingNotes()
    Server->>DB: SELECT notes WHERE status='pending'
    DB-->>Server: PendingNote[]
    Server-->>Moderator: Render Queue

    alt Approve Note
        Moderator->>Server: approveNote(noteId)
        Server->>DB: UPDATE status='approved'
        Server->>DB: createNotification('note_approved')
        Server->>Ext: Brevo.sendEmail(approval template)
        Server-->>Moderator: Success
    else Reject Note
        Moderator->>Server: rejectNote(noteId, reason)
        Server->>DB: UPDATE status='rejected'
        Server->>DB: createNotification('note_rejected')
        Server->>Ext: Brevo.sendEmail(rejection template)
        Server-->>Moderator: Success
    end

    %% AI Explanation Flow
    Note over Uploader,DB: 3. AI Explanation Flow (If Approved)
    Uploader->>Server: generateExplanation(noteId)
    Server->>DB: UPSERT ai_explanation (status='generating')
    Server->>Ext: Gemini Flash: generateObject(imageUrls)
    
    alt Success
        Ext-->>Server: Return structured JSON
        Server->>DB: UPDATE status='ready' & save JSON
        Server-->>Uploader: Return Explanation Data
    else Failure
        Ext--xServer: throw error
        Server->>DB: UPDATE status='failed'
        Server-->>Uploader: Return Error
    end
